#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/steam_mephit.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Death Burst.** When the mephit dies, it explodes in a cloud of steam. Each "
"creature within 5 feet of the mephit must succeed on a DC 10 Dexterity "
"saving throw or take 4 (1d8) fire damage.    \n"
"**Innate Spellcasting (1/Day)** The mephit can innately cast **_blur_**, "
"requiring no material components. Its innate spellcasting ability is "
"Charisma. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/steam_mephit.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions    \n"
"**Claws.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +2 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"creature. _Hit:_ 2 (1d4) slashing damage plus 2 (1d4) fire damage.    \n"
"**Steam Breath (Recharge 6).** The mephit exhales a 15- foot cone of "
"scalding steam. Each creature in that area must succeed on a DC 10 Dexterity "
"saving throw, taking 4 (1d8) fire damage on a failed save, or half as much "
"damage on a successful one.\n"
msgstr ""
